Chuvash National Broadcasting Company (CNBC, ) – broadcasting company of the Chuvash Republic. Autonomous Institution "National Broadcasting Company of Chuvashia" was created in December 2011 by the Cabinet of Ministers of the Chuvash Republic.
Founder – Ministry of Information and Mass Communications of the Chuvash Republic. The company includes: "Chuvash National Television", "Chuvash National Radio" and "Native Radio"
